<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/7081058-sha"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1484503062i/7081058._UY100_CR38,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/7081058-sha">Sha</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It&apos;s the first book of a standalone quartet that&apos;s related to the Bridgerton books and takes place at the same time. However, prior familiarity with t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It's the first book of a standalone quartet that's related to the Bridgerton books and takes place at the same time. However, prior familiarity with the Bridgerton books is only required for understanding obscure inside jokes, and not the main story.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
