<span id="freeTextContainer4609322575675638935">5 stars – Historical/Regency Romance<br/><br/><i>
  <b>Warning: May cause fits of giggles resulting in inquisitive stares if in public, an irrepressible smile to stay on your face, and cavities from too much sweetness.</b>
</i><br/><br/>This is such a cute, fun, charming, witty, feel-good read, and it was the perfect cure for my stressful, crummy week. It made me erupt with laughter several times, smile broadly throughout, and sigh in sheer delight at the romantic, sweet ending. <br/><br/>The <i>Bridgertons</i> hold a special place among my hist</span>
  <span id="freeText4609322575675638935" style="display:none">5 stars – Historical/Regency Romance<br /><br /><i>
  <b>Warning: May cause fits of giggles resulting in inquisitive stares if in public, an irrepressible smile to stay on your face, and cavities from too much sweetness.</b>
</i><br /><br />This is such a cute, fun, charming, witty, feel-good read, and it was the perfect cure for my stressful, crummy week. It made me erupt with laughter several times, smile broadly throughout, and sigh in sheer delight at the romantic, sweet ending. <br /><br />The <i>Bridgertons</i> hold a special place among my historical romance favorites, and the <i>Smythe-Smiths</i> promise to be another entertaining family with comical and romantic antics galore. <b>Just Like Heaven</b> is a heartwarming addition to my Julia Quinn keeper shelf. 5 sweet, heavenly stars!<br /><br /></span>
