          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8310179-blacky-romance-addict?shelf=4-stars-for-enjoyment">4-stars-for-enjoyment</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8310179-blacky-romance-addict?shelf=read-historical">read-historical</a>, 
