          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Mass Market Paperback 9780061491900" href="/book/show/9571478-just-like-heaven">review of another edition</a>

          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">fans of the Bridgertons books</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/171430-rivka?shelf=romance-and-womens-lit">romance-and-womens-lit</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/171430-rivka?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
